channel.title: Others cannot log in to my server
channel.description: I can log in only if i use the localhost ip adress, but if i use my real ip adress, i cannot. Chickenip says my ip adress is 76.3.124.86 and so does my No-ip program. My no-ip is forwarding 76.3.124.86 to jtscapepk.no-ip.info. How come i can get on mine with the local hosts but others cant? I have no router. thanks
